snippet.title: Catch & Release – Gameplay Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
This trailer shows the main gameplay aspects of Catch & Release: Explore the environment in your row boat, take in the beautiful scenery while you are looking for the perfect fishing spot. Throw out the hook and wait for a fish to bite. In the meantime, have a sandwich, listen to the radio or just relax. It‘s just you. On a Lake.

http://catchandrelease.game

Copyright metricminds GmbH & Co. KG
